Pro Kapital Grupp is listed on Nasdaq Baltic as well as on the Frankfurt Stock Exchange.
Last year, the group generated sales revenue of EUR 1,8 million in Lithuania and incurred losses of EUR 350 000, according to Pro Kapital Grupp's financial statements.
